FuncDef:
The any-flow command creates an Any-Flow view and displays the view, or displays an existing Any-Flow view.
The undo any-flow command deletes the Any-Flow view. The any-flow command creates an Any-Flow view and displays the view, or displays an existing Any-Flow view. The undo any-flow command deletes the Any-Flow view. By default, no Any-Flow view is created. This command is supported only on the CE6860-SAN, CE6866K, CE6866, CE6860-HAM, CE8850-SAN, CE8851K, CE8851-32CQ8DQ-P and CE8850-HAM.
